cts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/157890/', '', 'Citalopram, Sertraline, Fluoxetine, St. John''s Wort, Milnacipran, Vortioxetine, Levomilnacipran, Duloxetine, Viloxazine, Esketamine, Fluvoxamine, More', 'Alosetron, Isometheptene', 1767369485);
